name: Tupit
content:
Tupit was a female Bothan who lived with her brother named Galody in a home on Endor during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Tupit was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Tupit was added to the game along with the "IG-88" Heroic Encounter, introduced with the release of the "Chapter 7" update, on November 1, 2007.
